  "title": "Facilities Executive (Logistics MNC)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is from Freight Forwarding Industry. They are looking for a Facilities Executive to join their Facilities Management team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located in the East - easily accessible.</strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities of Facilities Executive:</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee day-to-day building operations and maintenance to ensure a safe, functional, and compliant facility.</li><li>Plan, schedule, and supervise maintenance, repair, and inspection activities.</li><li>Troubleshoot issues related to temperature/humidity (RH), power generators, chillers, air-conditioning systems, and other building equipment.</li><li>Coordinate with vendors and contractors on maintenance schedules and service delivery.</li><li>Ensure all contracts and service level agreements are properly managed and met.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Facilities Management or any related field</li><li>Minimum 3 years related technical experience, including troubleshooting in RH Temperature, Solar Panel, Power Generator, Air-Cond etc.</li><li>Comfortable with height and physically fit</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Email: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>RecruitPedia Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9682</p><p>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
